c XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>163BC</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Memphis</placeName>
<xref type="reprint from" targOrder="U" from="ROOT" to="DITTO" n="p.lond;1;24,r,p32" evaluate="all">PLond1,24p31;PForshall15</xref></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ Ἁρμάιος τῶν ἐν τῶι μεγάλωι Σαραπιείωι 

    <lb n="3"/>ὄντων ἐν κατοχῆι ἔτος πέμπτον, <choice><corr>διαζῶντος</corr><sic>διαζωντα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4"/>δὲ καὶ ἀφ᾽ ὧν ἐπαιτῶ ἐν τῶι ἱερῶι. ἀδικοῦμαι ὑπὸ 

    <lb n="5"/>Νεφόριτος τῶν ἀπὸ Μέμφεως. τοῦ γὰρ ταύτης 

    <lb n="6"/>θυγατρίου Ταθήμιος <choice><corr>συνδιατρίβοντος</corr><sic>συνδιατρι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λ</unclear>βοντος</sic></choice> ἐν τῶι 

    <lb n="7"/>ἱε<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρ</unclear>ῶι, <choice><corr>διαιτωμένου</corr><sic>διαιτωμενον</sic></choice> δὲ καὶ ἐξ ὧν ἐλόγευεν 

    <lb n="8"/>διὰ δομάτων, συναγαγούσης δὲ αὐτῆς <expan>χα<ex cert="high">λκοῦ</ex></expan> <num value="1300">Ατ</num> 

    <lb n="9"/>καὶ δούσης μοι αὐτὰς παραθήκην, μετὰ δέ τινα 

    <lb n="10"/>χρόνον τῆς Νεφόρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>τος παραλογισαμένης με 

    <lb n="11"/>καὶ προενεγκαμέ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>ης τὴν Ταθῆμιν ὥραν 

    <lb n="12"/>ἔχειν ὡς ἔθος ἐστὶ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> τοῖς Αἰγυπτίοις περι-

    <lb n="13"/><subst><add place="inline">τέμνεσθαι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">περι<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">τε</del>τεμνεσθαι</del></subst>, ἀξιωσά<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied>ης τ᾽ ἐμὲ δοῦναι αὐτῆι 

    <lb n="14"/>τὰς <num value="1300">Ατ</num>, ἐφ᾽ ὧι τοῦτ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied> ἐπιτελέσασα ἱματιεῖ αὐτὴν 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ ἐὰν ἐγ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δ</supplied>ῶται αὐτὴν ἀνδρὶ <choice><corr>φερ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>ιεῖ</corr><sic>φερ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>ιειν</sic></choice>, ἐὰν δὲ 

    <lb n="16"/>μὴ ποιῆι ἕκ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>στον τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ού</supplied>των ἢ καὶ μὴ περιτέμηι 

    <lb n="17"/>τὴν Ταθῆμ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>ν ἐν τῶ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied> Μεχεὶρ μηνὶ τοῦ <num value="18">ιη</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan>, 

    <lb n="18"/>ἀποτείσει <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μο</supplied>ι παραχρῆμα <expan>χα<ex cert="high">λκοῦ</ex></expan> <num value="2400">Βυ</num>, ἐφ᾽ οἷς συγχωρή-

    <lb n="19"/>σαντός μου καὶ δόντο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> αὐτῆι ἐν τῶι Θῶυθ μηνὶ 

    <lb n="20"/>τὰς <num value="1300">Ατ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan>, οὐδὲν τῶν διωμολογημένων <choice><corr>πεποίηκεν</corr><sic>πεποηκεν</sic></choice>, 

    <lb n="21"/>δι᾽ ἣν αἰτίαν περισπώμενος ὑπὸ τῆς Ταθήμιος 

    <lb n="22"/>καὶ ἀπαιτούμενος τὰς <num value="1300">Ατ</num> συμβαίνει μὴ δύνασθαι 

    <lb n="23"/>καταβῆναι εἰς Μέμφιν πρὸς ἀναγκαίας χρείας. 

    <lb n="24"/>ἀξιῶ οὖν σε μὴ <choice><corr><add place="supralinear">ὑ</add>περιδεῖν</corr><sic>περισπ</sic></choice> με περισπώμενον 

    <lb n="25"/>μισοπονηρῆσαί τε καὶ ἐφ᾽ οἷς διαπέπρακται 

    <lb n="26"/>ἐπὶ παραλογισμῶι, ἐάν σοι φαίνηται, συντάξαι 

    <lb n="27"/>ἀνακαλέσασθαι αὐτὴν ἐπὶ σὲ καὶ <choice><corr>ἂν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> ἦι οἷα γράφω, 

    <lb n="28"/>ἐπαναγκάσαι παραχρῆμα τὰ δίκαιά μοι <choice><corr>ποιῆσαι</corr><sic>ποησαι</sic></choice>, 

    <lb n="29"/>ὅπως καὶ αὐτὸς τῆι Ταθήμει ἀποδοὺς μὴ περισπῶμαι. 

    <lb n="30"/>τούτου δὲ γενομένου τεύξομαι βοηθείας. 

    <lb n="31"/>εὐτύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.3393" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3393" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="-0163-04-01" notAfter="-0163-10-03">1. Apr. - 3. Okt. 163 v.Chr. (Tage unsicher)</date></p></div><div n="meta.3393" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Rückseite: UPZ I 52. Zur Datierung vgl. Kongr. XVIII, S. 409-410 mit Anm. 16.</p></div><div n="meta.3393" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 17: <date type="mentioned" notBefore="-0163-03-02" notAfter="-0163-03-31">2. - 31. März 163 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3393" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">2</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">3393</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">2</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0245;1;2" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3393" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">499</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">362</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">X